_sText:
-basic ice world remake (similar concepts)
-invisible ladder to get up on the outside towers (in the corner)
-invisible ladder on middle columns (from start face the column and climb towards the light)
-buy zone in the center
-some objects you are able to wall through (depending on thickness of the object)
-fun to play with bots and other player

depending on ratings and votes another version may be made.
pm me if you have any ideas you want in the map, always welcome for ideas from players

thanks!

-unarmedhobo
